name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForChronicKidneyDiseases
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Chronic Kidney Diseases
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to chronic kidney disease and is listed as a renal disorder on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes chronic kidney disease including end stage renal disease. It also includes dual-diagnosis terms (e.g., hypertensive chronic kidney disease and hypertensive heart and chronic kidney disease).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes complications (e.g., Anemia in chronic kidney disease).)
